---
title: Italian Inspired Cheesy Pork Meatball Sub with Veggie 'Nduja, Pesto, Chips and Salad
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, this tasty Italian Inspired Cheesy Pork Meatball Sub is perfect for a casual sharing-style dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R31_W28_UK_SSF22810-3_Main_F1_high-1d069711.jpg
